{"about_the_game":"Breed the ultimate gun and struggle survive on a harsh planet!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>Guns!</strong></u></h2>Have you ever wanted your shotgun and your bazooka to procreate? Do you fantacize about your sniper and your machine gun gettin down and durty? In Wyrdgun not only is this a reality... its a necessity.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/Gungif2.gif?t=1698406363\" /><br>Every gun has 16 mutatable stats and can gain 32 additional special stats through breeding that greatly change the gun!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>Aliens!</strong></u></h2>Kill loads of freaks!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/Aliensgif.gif?t=1698406363\" /><br>Heaps of em!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>Planet!</strong></u></h2>Fight on an open world, procedurally generated, fully destructible, desert planet!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/Planetgif4.gif?t=1698406363\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>Mutations!</strong></u></h2>Gain wings, grappling webs, invisibility, and more.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/Mutationsgif.gif?t=1698406363\" /><br>Mutations are the progression system of Wyrdgun and persist across runs!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>Perks!</strong></u></h2>Wyrdgun has a modular perk system. Each perk contains a trigger and an effect. For example: hp is low =&gt; slow time, on kill =&gt; create a nova, or on dig =&gt; + digspeed!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/Perksgif.gif?t=1698406363\" /><br>There are 28 triggers and 45 effects to choose from!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"You rule!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommun